data.description: Updated price to sell.  Great location(1604 and Bandera), great neighborhood(Neighbors have been like family for seller), great low traffic street(at start of a cul-de-sac)! This one story, open floor plan is perfect for any family or entertaining. The home has a desireable layout with well thought out upgrades.  The large wooded blinds in each room are perfect for max sunlight  when opened or cozy energy saving privacy when closed. You will be captivated when you step out on the large deck in back yard! The greenbelt, although shrinking, is wonderful.  A solid shed and garden area complete an amazing back yard retreat.  Four bed rooms with ample storage is ready for you to move in.  Kitchen is open to the living room, making hosting get togethers easy, or keeping eye on TV while prepairing a meal.
